    "The DUT (TopModule) accumulates 1->0 edge detections in 'out' using a bitwise OR, but never clears bits after reset, causing stale edge captures to persist across resets [evidence: RTL L16 'out <= out | (prev_in & ~in);', L12-13 'out <= 32'b0; prev_in <= 32'b0;'] [evidence: log_excerpt L9 'Output 'out' has 91 mismatches. First mismatch occurred at time 140.']",
